title: Did Tyra Banks Really Just Announce That "America's Next Top Model" Is Canceled? (Please Say No, Tyra)
text:
Well this Tyramail came out of left field. Despite the fact that this season's Top Model has found arguably its most beautiful model in a while â€” Nyle DiMarco, come on down â€” and just recently aired an episode featuring a perfectly nonsensical music video promoting Tyra's new line of beauty products, it will apparently be the long-running reality show's last cycle. In a tweet this afternoon, Tyra said she's thinking it over, but "truly [believes] it's time" to end things. She has no more fucks photos left to give:
 TYRA MAIL!
Thinking #ANTM22 should be our last cycle. I truly believe it's time. May your pics be forever fierce. Keep on Smizing!
ðŸ’›Tyra
â€” Tyra Banks (@tyrabanks) October 14, 2015
Urgh , this is just the worst. I'm crying so hard right now it's like that challenge in cycle 6 where Tyra made the models cry except they used tear sticks to induce their emotion and that was cheating, really; my sadness is for real. Tyra, we were all rooting for you... to make this show last forever.
Reconsider, please!
